summary:
Requests 

(i) Transmission to MONUC of operational information for planning MONUC support for foreign troops withdrawal from DRC;

(ii) Transmission to MONUC of operational information for DDRRR programme planning for armed groups;

(iii) Direct dialogue between DRC and Rwanda governments for DDRRR coordination;

(iv) Establishment of conditions for voluntary DDRRR of armed groups members;

(v) Demilitarization of Kisangani;

(vi) Restoration of freedom of movement for persons and goods;

(vii) Full cooperation by parties with MONUC operations.
